<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span style="color:#707070">[ في الفرنسية]</span> Particulier ،essentiel ،propre ،subjectif<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
